author: Khaleda Rahman
title: Michigan Governor Gretchen Whitmer Says Protest Against Stay-at-Home Order Was a 'Political Rally'
description: Thousands of protesters gathered near the state capitol in Lansing, Michigan to voice their opposition to the stay-at-home order issued by Whitmer in response to the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Michigan Governor Gretchen Whitmer has hit back at the thousands of protesters who defied her stay-at-home order on Wednesday, saying the rally was "political" and had endangered people's lives.
